<i>noun</i>: 아랫도리 [아래또리/아랟또리] <br>
<ul>
<li><i>noun</i><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>아랫도리 [아래또리/아랟또리]</dt><br>
<dd>1. lower body; bottoms</dd><br>
<dd>허리의 아랫부분.</dd><br>
<dd>The part below the waist.</dd><br>
<dd>2. lower garment; bottom piece</dd><br>
<dd>아래에 입는 옷.</dd><br>
<dd>The clothes worn over one's lower body.</dd><br>
</li>
</ul>